{"tid":181838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾籌走數咖啡機兄弟再爆醜聞    今次係智能多士爐！","createTime":"2017-04-01T01:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T12:21:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b86f2defa43b7b959ef9be9900d0f4d4e55a206","tid":181838,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170401/56507003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170401%2F56507003&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=04e6ae41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170401%2F56507003&h=40660361\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170401/56507003</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490968412_7479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490968412_7479.jpg&h=d569a4db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以眾籌「走數」聞名國際的趙氏兄弟近日再惹抨擊，有外國博客發文質疑趙及有關人士除眾籌咖啡機Arist及磁能線Znaps外，亦涉與智能多士爐「Toasteroid」及手機轉換插「Auxillite」等另外2個眾籌項目關係密切，兩項目涉及金額約266萬港元。文中亦透露不少曾投資磁能線Znaps的網民，早前無故收到多士爐的宣傳電郵，質疑Znaps擅用客戶個人資料。趙氏、Toasteroid及Auxillite至截稿未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n該名為Dandesim的外國博客自稱是磁能線Znaps的苦主之一，至今仍未收到任何貨物，不過根據部份成功收貨的投資者上載相片，發貨地址正正位於香港科學園，與開發智能咖啡機、由趙氏持有的公司Nbition Development Limited註冊地址相同。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，早前作者亦無故收到另一眾籌項目、智能多士爐Toasteroid的宣傳電郵，由於電郵並非由眾籌網發出，故他即時停止訂閱（unsubscribe），系統卻隨即發出「你已從Znaps的28,000個投資者中移除」訊息；除他之外，Znaps的眾籌專頁亦有投資者留言投訴遇上同樣情況，質疑Znaps販賣客戶資料。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起作者懷疑，於是翻查多士爐的眾籌專頁，有關項目由「Chun Wai Matthew Yu」在去年8月發起，預計今年中發貨，地址位於紐約。其中，開發人員將多士爐的3D設計圖上載至Sketchfab網頁，惟作者發現，上載者竟以「nbition」作為其帳戶URL名稱，與趙氏的公司名相同。<br />\n<br />\n另一眾籌項目、手機轉換插頭Auxillite同樣由Chun Wai Matthew Yu發起，並已陸續發貨，惟被不少投資者投訴質素參次；也有人留言質問項目是否與Znaps有關，Auxillite則回覆否認，只稱曾委託「第三方營銷人員」作宣傳。本報就事件去信趙氏、Nbition、Toasteroid及Auxillite查詢，至截稿未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n趙氏的Nbition早年曾開托眾籌顧問服務，從中收取佣金，有關網頁現時已無法登入。上月趙公允亦曾應香港科技大學邀請，向學生舉辦「如何在24小時內為眾籌項目集資」講座，講座通告聲稱趙曾在眾籌平台「發起10多個成功項目，部份項目集資到7位數字的美金」。惟講座尚未舉行，先惹起社會爭議，最終科大取消講座。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指，咖啡機事件「聞名國際」，對本港初創企業的聲譽影響深遠，「好多外國公司再嚟香港揀startup都會好小心。」他續指，由於事件已糾纏2年，為避免事件繼續惡化，政府應介入調查，「睇下係唔係有啲詐騙成份。」⁠⁠⁠⁠<br />\n<br />\n若你有涉及公眾利益、權貴濫權等資料，請以WhatsApp、Line、Telegram或電郵方式聯絡《蘋果》調查組，我們有專人處理及跟進，內容絕對保密。"},{"pid":"cf488ab0f7874724c3747195e9523d3f9a923d26","tid":181838,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490965850_33a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490965850_33a3.jpg&h=22ab39f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙公允上月原應邀到科大舉行講座，惟因引起社會爭議被腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490965851_f3af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490965851_f3af.jpg&h=eb126cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nZnaps磁能線的信封上，指明貨物由香港科學園辦公室寄出，與趙氏的公司註冊地址相同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490965852_3e39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490965852_3e39.jpg&h=3b990f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機轉換插Auxillite<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490965853_390b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490965853_390b.jpg&h=74e66393&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智能多士爐Toasteroid<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490965849_41cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490965849_41cd.jpg&h=64eac580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智能多士爐Toasteroid的開發人員將3D圖片上載至Sketchfab網頁，卻使用「nbition」作為其帳戶URL名稱，與趙氏的公司名相同。"},{"pid":"f9a1d59dce6f0483eca25029afbd6c91a18d4440","tid":181838,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:48:32.000Z","msg":"有冇辦法可以唱到全世界， 咁落去盞比佢哋搞臭香港個名"},{"pid":"96a39fef0b74d61caccc3a6ff92298c89360f401","tid":181838,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:21:25.000Z","msg":"將來有套港產片，叫《眾籌夢幻》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c077205dbd654a4b8460b86d98b732716aa2e6d","tid":181838,"uid":33622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將來有套港產片，叫《眾籌夢幻》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫《大眾籌家》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce156da0e8500a47a5352349230dfcc4e1475b31","tid":181838,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"中國香港多騙徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf8c368e9c82b6dca52f1415e52aef0a7e4ab26","tid":181838,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"香港個朵臭晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c5d41a1b1d5382a321c37926134815bec28d69","tid":181838,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor